snippet.title: Mario's Picross 2 Easy Picross and Mario World 1 part 1
snippet.description:
(link to play below)

Oh god, this is much more difficult than the first game, mainly because I'm not used to puzzles of this size. It's disorienting. Hopefully I'll get used to it, because I aim to finish this game.

Also, the music in this game isn't nearly as good as in the first game. Far too short.

----------

Play Mario's Picross 2 for Game Boy Online: http://www.vizzed.com/playonlinegames/game.php?id=2170
